org.jsonurl.jsonorg

Interface JsonOrgValueFactory

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ValueFactory<Object,Object,JSONArray,JSONArray,JSONObject,JSONObject,Boolean,Number,Object,String>, ValueFactory.TransparentBuilder<Object,Object,JSONArray,JSONObject,Boolean,Number,Object,String>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    JsonOrgValueFactory.BigMathFactory

    public interface JsonOrgValueFactory
extends ValueFactory.TransparentBuilder<Object,Object,JSONArray,JSONObject,Boolean,Number,Object,String>
    A JSON→URL ValueFactory which uses classes from the org.json package.
